# dc877ba44cf54fe6b69a6733fd76d363
msgid "You can also create \"virtual columns\" that contain combinations of the metadata from other columns. In the add column dialog  use the :guilabel:`Quick create` links to easily create columns to show the book ISBN, formats or the time the book was last modified. For more details, see :ref:`templatelangcalibre`."
