#: ../../faq.rst:770
# 79be5a10dfe34072be5e3366d8e2bae5
msgid "If you use RoboForm, it is known to cause |app| to crash. Add |app| to the blacklist of programs inside RoboForm to fix this. Or uninstall RoboForm."
